e's the modified code that allows you to search for conversation titles based on the provided template:\\n\\n```html\\n<p>Start typing to search for conversation titles</p>\\n<$edit-text tiddler=\\\"SearchFor\\\" field=\\\"text\\\"/><p/>\\n<$vars searchfor=SearchFor>\\nFound <$count filter=\\\"[tag[chatgptmessage]search:text<searchfor>sort[title]each[conversation_id]]\\\"/>\\nwith \\\"<$text text=SearchFor$>\\\"\\n<hr>\\n<$list filter=\\\"[tag[chatgptmessage]search:text<searchfor>sort[title]each[conversation_id]]\\\">\\n    <b><$view field=\\\"conversation_title\\\"/></b>\\n    <$link>Message</$link> \\n    <$link to=<<currentTiddler>>>Conversation</$link><hr>\\n</$list>\\n</$vars>\\n```\\n\\nThis code snippet allows users to search for conversation titles based on the provided template. It displays the count of conversations found with the searched title and provides links to the corresponding messages and conversations.\"]},\"create_time\":1717438816.676264,\"end_turn\":true,\"id\":\"5414ea3b-345c-4ee2-b791-68a72b9ed747\",\"metadata\":{\"citations\":[],\"default_model_slug\":\"text-davinci-002-render-sha\",\"finish_details\":{\"stop_tokens\":[100260],\"type\":\"stop\"},\"gizmo_id\":null,\"is_complete\":true,\"message_type\":null,\"model_slug\":\"text-davinci-002-render-sha\",\"model_switcher_deny\":[],\"parent_id\":\"34bf1d14-27f2-459e-adf1-fc3588c8f0b3\",\"request_id\":\"88e1b2267ec61809-EWR\",\"timestamp_\":\"absolute\"},\"recipient\":\"all\",\"status\":\"finished_successfully\",\"update_time\":null,\"weight\":1},\"parent\":\"34bf1d14-27f2-459e-adf1-fc3588c8f0b3\"},\"62275116-4e72-4cdc-a0cf-68bc6f34a599\":{\"children\":[\"de689841-7b3f-4446-b886-fb833a71c91c\"],\"id\":\"62275116-4e72-4cdc-a0cf-68bc6f34a599\",\"message\":{\"author\":{\"metadata\":{},\"name\":\"\",\"role\":\"user\"},\"content\":{\"content_type\":\"text\",\"parts\":[\"that changed nothing\"]},\"create_time\":1717438666.291812,\"end_turn\":null,\"id\":\"62275116-4e72-4cdc-a0cf-68bc6f34a599\",\"metadata\":{\"message_source\":null,\"message_type\":null,\"request_id\":\"88e1ae8ef8af42ad-EWR\",\"timestamp_\":\"absolute\"},\"recipient\":\"all\",\"status\":\"finished_successfully\",\"update_time\":null,\"weight\":1},\"parent\":\"0b6e6b02-6a93-4a44-9b10-fe59a1719312\"},\"7ce94fff-068e-4f53-947d-54bde61a82cb\":{\"children\":[\"0b6e6b02-6a93-4a44-9b10-fe59a1719312\"],\"id\":\"7ce94fff-068e-4f53-947d-54bde61a82cb\",\"message\":{\"author\":{\"metadata\":{},\"name\":\"\",\"role\":\"user\"},\"content\":{\"content_type\":\"text\",\"parts\":[\"its displaying this \\\"Found 1 with \\\"SearchFor$\\\"\"]},\"create_time\":1717438646.934335,\"end_turn\":null,\"id\":\"7ce94fff-068e-4f53-947d-54bde61a82cb\",\"metadata\":{\"message_source\":null,\"message_type\":null,\"request_id\":\"88e1ae153d3842ad-EWR\",\"timestamp_\":\"absolute\"},\"recipient\":\"all\",\"status\":\"finished_successfully\",\"update_time\":null,\"weight\":1},\"parent\":\"0aee04ce-a0a9-4097-802c-f5346e3d74f6\"},\"9b7500f0-b21b-4a05-94f2-c64b49d1288e\":{\"children\":[\"09cefe95-43e5-4c7e-bd22-578e61bf7576\"],\"id\":\"9b7500f0-b21b-4a05-94f2-c64b49d1288e\",\"message\":{\"author\":{\"metadata\":{},\"name\":null,\"role\":\"assistant\"},\"content\":{\"content_type\":\"text\",\"parts\":[\"To create a search function based on conversation title using the provided templates, you can follow these steps:\\n\\n1. Create a new tiddler named \\\"Search by Conversation Title\\\" or any suitable name.\\n2. In this new tiddler, define the search interface where users can input the conversation title they want to search for.\\n3. Use a `$list` widget to filter conversations based on the input title.\\n4. Display the search results using the conversation template.\\n\\nHere's how you can implement it:\\n\\n```html\\n\\\\define search-by-title()\\n<div class=\\\"search-form\\\">\\n    <form>\\n        <label for=\\\"conversation-title\\\">Search by Conversation Title:</label><br>\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" id=\\\"conversation-title\\\" name=\\\"conversation-title\\\"><br><br>\\n        <input type=\\\"button\\\" value=\\\"Search\\\" onclick=\\\"searchByTitle()\\\">\\n    </form>\\n</div>\\n\\n<script>\\nfunction searchByTitle() {\\n    var title = document.getElementById(\\\"conversation-title\\\").value;\\n    // Redirect to search result tiddler with title parameter\\n    window.location.href = \\\"#SearchResults_\\\" + title;\\n}\\n</script>\\n\\n\\\\end\\n\\n\\\\define search-results()\\n<div class=\\\"search-results\\\">\\n    <$list filter=\\\"[is[current]conversation-hub]\\\">\\n        <$list filter=\\\"[title[SearchResults_$:/temp/conversation-title]]\\\">\\n            <$list filter=\\\"[conversation_title{!!conversation_title}]\\\">\\n                <<annotation-tiddler>> <!-- Include annotation -->\\n                <<annotation-header-text>> <!-- Include header text -->\\n                <!-- Include conversation navigation buttons -->\\n                <!-- Include conversation messages -->\\n            </$list>\\n        </$list>\\n    </$list>\\n</div>\\n\\\\end\\n\\n<<search-by-title>>\\n<<search-results>>\\n```\\n\\nWith this setup, users can enter a conversation title in the search form. When they click the \\\"Search\\\" button, it triggers the `searchByTitle()` JavaScript function, which redirects to a new tiddler titled \\\"SearchResults_ConversationTitle\\\" (e.g., \\\"SearchResults_MyConversation\\\"). In this new tiddler, the search results will be displayed based on the entered conversation title.\"]},\"create_time\":1717438378.565187,\"end_turn\":true,\"id\":\"9b7500f0-b21b-4a05-94f2-c64b49d1288e\",\"metadata\":{\"citations\":[],\"default_model_slug\":\"text-davinci-002-render-sha\",\"finish_details\":{\"stop_tokens\":[100260],\"type\":\"stop\"},\"gizmo_id\":null,\"is_complete\":true,\"message_type\":null,\"model_slug\":\"text-davinci-002-render-sha\",\"model_switcher_deny\":[],\"pad\":\"AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA\",\"parent_id\":\"c82cebae-7c89-40dc-afad-37138e0de21c\",\"request_id\":\"88e1a7605b0143b3-EWR\",\"timestamp_\":\"absolute\"},\"recipient\":\"all\",\"status\":\"finished_successfully\",\"update_time\":null,\"weight\":1},\"parent\":\"c82cebae-7c89-40dc-afad-37138e0de21c\"},\"c82cebae-7c89-40dc-afad-37138e0de21c\":{\"children\":[\"9b7500f0-b21b-4a05-94f2-c64b49d1288e\"],\"id\":\"c82cebae-7c89-40dc-afad-37138e0de21c\",\"message\":{\"author\":{\"metadata\":{},\"name\":\"\",\"role\":\"user\"},\"content\":{\"content_type\":\"text\",\"parts\":[\"\\\"\\\\define annotation-tiddler() Annotation-$(tiddler-title)$\\n\\\\define annotation-header-text() $(conversation_title)$ message $(conversation_index)$\\n\\n\\n<div class=\\\"hub\\\">\\n\\n<$list filter=\\\"[is[current]chatarchivist[conversation-hub]]\\\">\\n<$vars conversation_index= first=\\\"1\\\" conversation_title= tiddler-title= >\\n<$set name=\\\"previous\\\" filter=\\\"[<conversation_index>subtract[1]]\\\">\\n<$set name=\\\"next\\\" filter=\\\"[<conversation_index>add[1]]\\\">\\n<$set name=\\\"last\\\" filter=\\\"[file_hash{!!file_hash}chatarchivist[]count[]]\\\">\\n\\n\\n\\n<div class=\\\"tc-tiddler-title\\\">\\n<div class=\\\"tc-titlebar\\\">\\n\\n<div class=\\\"conversation-title\\\">\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n<div class=\\\"conversation-navigation\\\">\\nSelect message # to show <$button>First (#<<first>>)\\n<$action-setfield $tiddler= conversation_index=1/>\\n<$action-navigate $to=/>\\n</$button>\\n make this type of JSON file compatible with the already written script